Self-Checkout Usage Analysis

Self-Checkout Usage by Time Period

In this section, we visualize the average self-checkout usage across different time periods.

Self-Checkout Usage by Time Period

Key Findings:

  • The self-checkout usage rate is highest in the morning and midday periods.

Item Quantity and Self-Checkout Rate

We show how the number of items in the cart influences self-checkout usage.

Item Quantity and Self-Checkout Rate

Key Findings:

  • Shoppers with fewer items in their cart are more likely to use self-checkout.

Self-Checkout Usage by Group Size

This section shows how the group size influences the likelihood of choosing self-checkout.

Self-Checkout Usage by Group Size

Key Findings:

  • Shoppers shopping alone are more likely to use self-checkout.
